2. In the scene, create a new KinematicBody-node (under the Physics3D > Kinematic category). This will be our player character.
3. Create a new script (under the Scripts > GDScript category) and open it in the editor.
4. In the script, define a new node path (either through the $SceneTree variable or by creating it programmatically) for the KinematicBody-node that will control the player character.
